upports WoL / System Power Controls','http://www.phoronix.com/vr.php?view=MTg0NzA',NULL,'2014-11-25 03:09:37','More exciting code continues to be pushed into the Phoronix Test Suite 5.4-Lipki Git repository ahead of its planned stable debut next week...'),(28,11,'Crowdfunding','http://completelyseriouscomics.com/?p=799','Jesse','2014-11-24 09:01:00','<p><a href=\"http://completelyseriouscomics.com/?p=799\" title=\"Ain\'t they the cutest\"><img src=\"http://completelyseriouscomics.com//comics/2014-11-24-Doodles.jpg\" alt=\"Ain\'t they the cutest\" class=\"comicthumbnail\" title=\"Ain\'t they the cutest\" />\n</a></p>HEY KIDS I found some comics from when the Patreon existed so I decided to make this site still exist and post them'),(29,12,'Lipki\'s Phoromatic Now Supports WoL / System Power Controls','http://www.phoronix.com/vr.php?view=MTg0NzA',NULL,'2014-11-25 03:09:37','More exciting code continues to be pushed into the Phoronix Test Suite 5.4-Lipki Git repository ahead of its planned stable debut next week...'),(30,13,'Lipki\'s Phoromatic Now Supports WoL / System Power Controls','http://www.phoronix.com/vr.php?view=MTg0NzA',NULL,'2014-11-25 03:09:37','More exciting code continues to be pushed into the Phoronix Test Suite 5.4-Lipki Git repository ahead of its planned stable debut next week...'),(31,14,'Lipki\'s Phoromatic Now Supports WoL / System Power Controls','http://www.phoronix.com/vr.php?view=MTg0NzA',NULL,'2014-11-25 03:09:37','More exciting code continues to be pushed into the Phoronix Test Suite 5.4-Lipki Git repository ahead of its planned stable debut next week...'),(32,15,'Lipki\'s Phoromatic Now Supports WoL / System Power Controls','http://www.phoronix.com/vr.php?view=MTg0NzA',NULL,'2014-11-25 03:09:37','More exciting code continues to be pushed into the Phoronix Test Suite 5.4-Lipki Git repository ahead of its planned stable debut next week...'),(33,16,'Lipki\'s Phoromatic Now Supports WoL / System Power Controls','http://www.phoronix.com/vr.php?view=MTg0NzA',NULL,'2014-11-25 03:09:37','More exciting code continues to be pushed into the Phoronix Test Suite 5.4-Lipki Git repository ahead of its planned stable debut next week...'),(34,17,'Like the blog? Get the book: http://amzn.to/1odgBgK','http://1000lifehacks.com/post/103499389903',NULL,'2014-11-25 00:40:40','<img src=\"http://33.media.tumblr.com/b8e1c231a1e010c6ff5a20fce68f593f/tumblr_nfk0ht6Hfq1sa4vz3o1_500.png\"/><br/><br/><p><span>Like the blog? Get the book: </span><span></span><a href=\"http://amzn.to/1odgBgK\" target=\"_blank\">http://amzn.to/1odgBgK</a></p>'),(35,18,'Apple OS X 10.10 vs. Ubuntu 14.10 Performance','http://www.phoronix.com/vr.php?view=21179',NULL,'2014-11-25 16:30:00','While I delivered some OS X 10.10 Yosemite preview benchmarks back in August, here\'s my first tests of the official release of Apple OS X 10.10.1 compared to Ubuntu 14.10 Linux. Tests were done of OS X 10.9.5 and OS X 10.10.1 against Ubuntu 14.10 Utopic Unicorn when running the benchmarks under both GCC and LLVM Clang compilers.'),(36,19,'Like the blog? Get the book: http://amzn.to/1odgBgK','http://1000lifehacks.com/post/103499389903',NULL,'2014-11-25 00:40:40','<img src=\"http://33.media.tumblr.com/b8e1c231a1e010c6ff5a20fce68f593f/tumblr_nfk0ht6Hfq1sa4vz3o1_500.png\"/><br/><br/><p><span>Like the blog? Get the book: </span><span></span><a href=\"http://amzn.to/1odgBgK\" target=\"_blank\">http://amzn.to/1odgBgK</a></p>'),(37,20,'Photo','http://lolthatsme.tumblr.com/post/103500174848',NULL,'2014-11-25 00:51:03','<img src=\"http://38.media.tumblr.com/06e766bc65536ef3d330fbce5c348c86/tumblr_nfki935O921rrqglzo1_500.gif\"/><br/><br/>'),(38,21,'Photo','http://lolthatsme.tumblr.com/post/103500174848',NULL,'2014-11-25 00:51:03','<img src=\"http://38.media.tumblr.com/06e766bc65536ef3d330fbce5c348c86/tumblr_nfki935O921rrqglzo1_500.gif\"/><br/><br/>'),(39,22,'Photo','http://lolthatsme.tumblr.com/post/103500174848',NULL,'2014-11-25 00:51:03','<img src=\"http://38.media.tumblr.com/06e766bc65536ef3d330fbce5c348c86/tumblr_nfki935O921rrqglzo1_500.gif\"/><br/><br/>'),(40,23,'Photo','http://lolthatsme.tumblr.com/post/103500174848',NULL,'2014-11-25 00:51:03','<img src=\"http://38.media.tumblr.com/06e766bc65536ef3d330fbce5c348c86/tumblr_nfki935O921rrqglzo1_500.gif\"/><br/><br/>'),(41,24,'Changes to Intel microcode updates','https://www.archlinux.org/news/changes-to-intel-microcodeupdates/','Thomas Bächler','2014-10-22 23:29:10','<p>Microcode on Intel CPUs is no longer loaded automatically, as it needs\nto be loaded very early in the boot process. This requires adjustments\nin the bootloader. If you have an Intel CPU, please follow <a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Microcode#Enabling_Intel_Microcode_Updates\">the\ninstructions in the\nwiki</a>.</p>');
